      • useDialogForExpirationDateEntry

        public void useDialogForExpirationDateEntry(android.app.Activity activity,
                                            boolean useDialog)
        Used to enable or disable entry of the expiration date using ExpirationDateDialog. Defaults to false.
        Parameters:
        activity - used as the parent activity for the dialog
        useDialog - false to use a numeric keyboard to enter the expiration date, true to use a custom dialog to enter the expiration date. Defaults to true.
